Package: aisdk.shiny
Title: Shiny Web Interface for the 'aisdk' Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny-based web chat interface and configuration UI for the 'aisdk'
    toolkit. Provides ready-to-use Shiny modules and a server runtime for
    interactive, streaming conversations with AI models, including a model
    configuration panel and an optional 'shinychat' backend.
