        digest, jsonlite, rlang
Suggests: shinychat, DT, curl, R6, withr, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.shiny
BugReports: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.shiny/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
